{"tid":626193,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"拉莫斯或面臨追加禁賽 12碼爭議時 他走到祖記區域和對方職員發生衝突","createTime":"2018-04-12T02:34:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T02:46:23.000Z","uid":54373,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0959f0616e726060df8916d5f9c7b667249480cd","tid":626193,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T02:34:39.000Z","msg":"2018年04月12日07:13<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2018/04/12/2/2bd99f3b2fd3f2ef6ecf818455c972d6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2018%2F04%2F12%2F2%2F2bd99f3b2fd3f2ef6ecf818455c972d6.jpg&h=5dff5e2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n拉莫斯出現在球員通道<br />\n<br />\n　　皇馬與祖記的比賽，比賽最後時刻發生了戲劇性的一幕。皇馬傷停補時獲得12碼，祖記不滿球證的判罰，雙方陷入爭吵。場邊的拉莫斯也跟祖記的工作人員發生衝突。<br />\n<br />\n　　按照規定，處在停賽期的球員不允許出現在球場邊上，無法進入後備席，這些都被視為是停賽的一部分。《馬卡報》透露，如果球證將拉莫斯寫入球證報告，那麼他可能面臨新的一輪停賽。<br />\n<br />\n　　《阿斯報》表示，拉莫斯可能錯過首回合4強比賽。因為累積黃牌停賽，拉莫斯無緣今場與祖記的強強對話。但是最後時刻，拉莫斯為了鼓勵隊友，出現在球場邊，這違法了相關規定。因此，拉莫斯可能遭到另一場停賽。"},{"pid":"a34e7eebb64b9b1f86d03d5058713b840079b7dc","tid":626193,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T02:37:04.000Z","msg":"停賽仲衝入球場打9人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f29eaf5369be9b47694e9e76100600f41a034a4a","tid":626193,"uid":145365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a34e7eebb64b9b1f86d03d5058713b840079b7dc","tid":626193,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T02:37:04.000Z","msg":"停賽仲衝入球場打9人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T02:46:23.000Z","msg":"係囉 抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}